# Images belong here: photos, icons, logos, favicons, Open Graph images.
#
# Tips for Core Web Vitals:
#   - Use modern formats (.webp or .avif) with a .jpg/.png fallback if needed.
#   - Always set width/height (or aspect-ratio) on <img> to avoid layout shift.
#   - Use loading="lazy" for below-the-fold images; NOT on the hero/LCP image.
#   - Provide a favicon.ico, favicon.svg and apple-touch-icon.png (referenced
#     in every page <head>).
#
# This file only exists so Git tracks the otherwise-empty folder. It can be
# deleted once real images are added.
